Project: Transport Network System
The Ministry of Transport contacted and supplied Group 2 at TransRoute Systems with cities and road networks, real-time traffic updates, and delivery request stream. The group was asked to create a model of the map, reroute based on live traffic condtions, and track deliveries. 
System requirements paresed by the team are:
  Adding new roads and cities to a map
  Update and retrieve the distance (or cost) of roads
  Handle dynamic traffic reports
  Find the shortest path between cities
  Schedule and record deliveries
  Undo schedule and record

Contribution Breakdown
